sub_title: Anthropologist researching unequal power dynamics and business ethics.
summary:
✚ I aim to unravel systemic social inequalities and (corporate) power dynamics with an intersectional approach. 
✚ International research experience, including extensive fieldwork on: 
- The manifestation of western discourses such as Social Impact, Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) and entrepreneurship in Sudan. 
- The reintegration of former combatants in Colombia.
✚ Passionate about whistleblower protection, accountability, corporate inclusion and true representation.
